<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Phase 1: Run with AppDynamics on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ninja-workshops/17-appd-ingest/2-run-with-appd/</link><description>Recent content in Phase 1: Run with AppDynamics on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ninja-workshops/17-appd-ingest/2-run-with-appd/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>1. Build the App</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ninja-workshops/17-appd-ingest/2-run-with-appd/1-build-the-app/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ninja-workshops/17-appd-ingest/2-run-with-appd/1-build-the-app/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The workshop includes a simple Spring Boot application with a few REST endpoints. Let&amp;rsquo;s build it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="verify-java-and-maven"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;Verify Java and Maven&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#verify-java-and-maven" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your instance has OpenJDK 17 and Maven pre-installed. Confirm:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="tabs" data-tabs&gt;
&lt;div class="tabs__list" role="tablist"&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-0" class="tabs__btn is-active" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-0" tabindex="0" data-tab-label="Command"&gt;Command&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-1" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-1" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Example Output"&gt;Example Output&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id="tabs-0-panel-0" class="tabs__panel is-active" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabs-0-tab-0" data-tab-label="Command"&gt;&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;java -version &lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; mvn -version&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id="tabs-0-panel-1" class="tabs__panel" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabs-0-tab-1" hidden data-tab-label="Example Output"&gt;&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;text&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;openjdk version &amp;#34;17.0.x&amp;#34; ...
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;Apache Maven 3.x.x ...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2 id="build-the-application"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;Build the Application&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#build-the-application" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Navigate to the workshop app directory and build the fat JAR:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>2. Download the AppD Agent</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ninja-workshops/17-appd-ingest/2-run-with-appd/2-download-appd-agent/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ninja-workshops/17-appd-ingest/2-run-with-appd/2-download-appd-agent/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;You need the AppDynamics Java Agent (version 25.6.0 or higher) to use dual signal mode. We&amp;rsquo;ll add it to your instance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="unzip-the-agent"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;Unzip the Agent&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#unzip-the-agent" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SSH into your instance, run the download script, and the agent will be extracted to the &lt;code&gt;agent&lt;/code&gt; directory we created:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; ~/workshop/appd
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;mkdir -p agent
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;chmod +x ./download-appd-agent.sh
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;./download-appd-agent.sh&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You should now have the agent JAR at &lt;code&gt;~/workshop/appd/agent/javaagent.jar&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="note-your-account-access-key"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;Note Your Account Access Key&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#note-your-account-access-key" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&amp;rsquo;ll need the &lt;a href="https://se-lab.saas.appdynamics.com/controller/#/licensing/license-management-account?timeRange=last_15_minutes.BEFORE_NOW.-1.-1.15" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Account Access Key&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;span aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:0.75em;opacity:0.6;"&gt;&amp;#x2197;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
 when running the app. You can find it in the AppDynamics Controller:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>3. Run and Verify in AppD</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ninja-workshops/17-appd-ingest/2-run-with-appd/3-run-and-verify/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/ninja-workshops/17-appd-ingest/2-run-with-appd/3-run-and-verify/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Now run the application with the AppDynamics agent attached. This is the &amp;ldquo;normal&amp;rdquo; single-destination instrumentation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="run-with-the-appdynamics-agent"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;Run with the AppDynamics Agent&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#run-with-the-appdynamics-agent" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Replace &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;YOUR-ACCESS-KEY&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; with the AppDynamics token from the previous step:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="tabs" data-tabs&gt;
&lt;div class="tabs__list" role="tablist"&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-0" class="tabs__btn is-active" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-0" tabindex="0" data-tab-label="Command"&gt;Command&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-1" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-1" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Example"&gt;Example&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id="tabs-0-panel-0" class="tabs__panel is-active" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabs-0-tab-0" data-tab-label="Command"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Export your environment variables&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;export&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nv"&gt;APPD_ACCESS_KEY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;Your-AppDynamics-access-key&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;and&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;export&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nv"&gt;APPD_APP_NAME&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;Dual-Ingest-&lt;span class="si"&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;INSTANCE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="si"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Then we can start java with the agent:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; ~/workshop/appd
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;java -javaagent:agent/javaagent.jar &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -Dappdynamics.controller.hostName&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;se-lab.saas.appdynamics.com &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -Dappdynamics.controller.port&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;443&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -Dappdynamics.controller.ssl.enabled&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -Dappdynamics.agent.applicationName&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="si"&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;APPD_APP_NAME&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="si"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -Dappdynamics.agent.tierName&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;OrderService &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -Dappdynamics.agent.nodeName&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;OrderService-Node &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -Dappdynamics.agent.accountName&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;se-lab &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -Dappdynamics.agent.accountAccessKey&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="si"&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;APPD_ACCESS_KEY&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="si"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -jar app/target/ingest-workshop-1.0.0.jar &lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id="tabs-0-panel-1" class="tabs__panel" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabs-0-tab-1" hidden data-tab-label="Example"&gt;&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;text&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;java -javaagent:agent/javaagent.jar \
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -Dappdynamics.controller.hostName=se-lab.saas.appdynamics.com \
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -Dappdynamics.controller.port=443 \
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -Dappdynamics.controller.ssl.enabled=true \
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -Dappdynamics.agent.applicationName=Dual-Ingest-shw-4267 \
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -Dappdynamics.agent.tierName=OrderService \
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -Dappdynamics.agent.nodeName=OrderService-Node \
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -Dappdynamics.agent.accountName=se-lab \
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -Dappdynamics.agent.accountAccessKey=&amp;#34;hj9999999999&amp;#34; \
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; -jar app/target/ingest-workshop-1.0.0.jar &amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Wait for the Spring Boot startup banner to appear (about 10-15 seconds).
Press return to go back to your prompt.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>